{"word":"G505 - ἀνυπόκριτος - anypókritos - an-oo-pok'-ree-tos - Without dissimulation","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">ἀνυπόκριτος</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">anypókritos</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">an-oo-pok'-ree-tos</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Without dissimulation</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Adjective / பெயரடை</span>"},{"paragraph":"மாயமற்ற - பெயரடை"},{"paragraph":"unfeigned, undisguised"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>From <a href=\"#/G1 - Α - A - al'-fah/1\">G1</a> (as a negative particle) and a presumed derivative of <a href=\"#/G5271 - ὑποκρίνομαι - hypokrínomai - hoop-ok-rin'-om-ahee/5271\">G5271</a>; <i>undissembled</i>, that is, <i>sincere:</i> - without dissimulation (hypocrisy), unfeigned.</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>தொடர்புடைய எண்கள் / Cognate: </strong><a href=\"#/G4942/4942\">G4942</a>, <a href=\"#/G505/505\">G505</a>, <a href=\"#/G5271/5271\">G5271</a>, <a href=\"#/G5272/5272\">G5272</a>, <a href=\"#/G5273/5273\">G5273</a>"}]}